<br>
I had to charm a named scorpion, Impaler Tzilug, who sits in a room near the zone to Howling Stones. He is in a large room with 4 other guardians and there is one more who wanders.<br>
<br>
Falidar read out the info on Allakhazam... several ways had been tried. We tried two that failed for us. Amazine rezzed me twice (or was it three times?)<br>
<br>
Amazine and Falidar talked while I was gone (LD), and when I came back they had a careful plan all worked out. We'd try plan A, and had B as a backup... all 3 of us had jobs to do to get it done. In the end, luck blessed us and it went smoothly.<br>
<br>
