<br>
Amazine had bound herself near the OT crevice to help rez herself if she had to. Thank goodness it wasn't needed. BUT I know what a pain it was for her to find a port or run back... <br>
<br>
Falidar stayed on much longer than I think he had planned but he was more determined than I to stay and get it done.<br>
<br>
/bow<br>
/salute<br>
/thanks<br>
/hugs<br>
<br>
THANK YOU BOTH ! You both demonstrated great integrity, kindness, selflessness and generosity. You are both great examples of what a knight should be. I hope I can return the favor for each of you sometime too.<br>
<br>
A very thankful, and tired-out <br>
Chanterin<br>
